flowchart TD
    A[Customer booking created] --> B[Booking validation and supplier confirmation]
    B --> C[Booking stored in operational database]
    C --> D[Invoice generated for customer]
    C --> E[Commission calculated based on supplier rules]
    D --> F[AR journal entry created automatically]
    E --> G[Commission accrual journal entry created]
    D --> H[Payment request sent to Stripe or PayPal]
    H --> I[Payment captured webhook received]
    I --> J[Payment recorded and invoice updated]
    J --> K[Cash receipt journal entry created]
    C --> L[Supplier payable recognized]
    L --> M[Supplier settlement batch processed]
    M --> N[AP settlement journal entry created]
    F --> O[Reporting projections refreshed]
    G --> O
    K --> O
    N --> O
    O --> P[SST and GST financial outputs available]
